 he was not present at the concerned body and directed him to immediately appear at the concerned body and assist in the investigation.","title":"UML suspends Top Bahadur Rayamajhi","url":"http://english.ratopati.com/story/27697/uml-suspends-top-bahadur-","video":[]}
